title: This video of three old women doing ‘Bhangra’ is the best thing you will see on internet today
text:
Reviews Search for: This video of three old women doing ‘Bhangra’ is the best thing you will see on internet today February 23, 2017, 9:02 pm IST Team Social in Everything Social | World | TOI 
Age is just a number. This is not a concept and these three old women are out to prove it. 
How often do you find old women shaking a leg on popular dance numbers? Forget that, how often do you find them doing ‘Bhangra’? 
This video which is going viral shows that old people sure know how to have fun. And if you are having a bad day, it is bound to lift your spirits.
